---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us - JSON Formatter Pro"
  description="Get in touch with the JSON Formatter Pro team. Send us your questions, feedback, or support requests."
  path="/contact"
  keywords="contact, support, feedback, help, customer service"
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-fg">Contact Us</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-subtle">
      Have a question or feedback? We'd love to hear from you. Get in touch using any of the methods below.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-fg">📧 Email</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-subtle">
          For general inquiries and support requests:
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:support@json-formatter-pro.com"
          class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary hover:underline"
        >
          support@json-formatter-pro.com →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-fg">💬 GitHub</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-subtle">
          Report bugs or discuss features:
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/json-formatter-pro/issues"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="mt-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary hover:underline"
        >
          Open an issue →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-fg">⏱️ Response Time</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-subtle">
          We typically respond to inquiries within 48 hours during business days.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-fg">🏢 Address</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-subtle">
          JSON Formatter Pro<br />
          Remote-first Organization
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface p-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-fg">Frequently Asked Contact Questions</h2>

      <details class="mt-6 border-t border-border pt-6" open>
        <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-4 text-base font-medium text-fg">
          <span>What should I do if the formatter isn't working correctly?</span>
          <span class="text-subtle transition-transform">−</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-subtle">
          First, try clearing your browser cache and localStorage. If the issue persists, please email us at support@json-formatter-pro.com with:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-sm text-subtle">
          <li>A description of the issue</li>
          <li>Steps to reproduce</li>
          <li>Your browser and OS (e.g., Chrome on macOS)</li>
          <li>A sample JSON file that triggers the issue (if applicable)</li>
        </ul>
      </details>

      <details class="border-t border-border pt-6">
        <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-4 text-base font-medium text-fg">
          <span>How do I report a security issue?</span>
          <span class="text-subtle transition-transform">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-subtle">
          Please do not disclose security vulnerabilities publicly. Instead, email security@json-formatter-pro.com with details of the issue. We'll investigate and respond promptly.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="border-t border-border pt-6">
        <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-4 text-base font-medium text-fg">
          <span>Can I request a new feature?</span>
          <span class="text-subtle transition-transform">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-subtle">
          Absolutely! We welcome feature requests. You can:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6 text-sm text-subtle">
          <li>Open a GitHub issue with the label "feature-request"</li>
          <li>Email us at support@json-formatter-pro.com</li>
        </ul>
      </details>

      <details class="border-t border-border pt-6">
        <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-4 text-base font-medium text-fg">
          <span>Do you offer enterprise or custom solutions?</span>
          <span class="text-subtle transition-transform">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-subtle">
          For enterprise inquiries, licensing questions, or custom development, please contact us at enterprise@json-formatter-pro.com.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="border-t border-border pt-6">
        <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between gap-4 text-base font-medium text-fg">
          <span>How do I report abuse or policy violations?</span>
          <span class="text-subtle transition-transform">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-subtle">
          If you believe someone is using JSON Formatter Pro in violation of our Terms of Service or for illegal purposes, please report it to abuse@json-formatter-pro.com with details.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
